────────────────────────────────────────────────

📋 DESCRIPTION
Sensitivity analysis for causal mediation effects
under differential misclassification (recall bias,
outcome-dependent measurement error).

Implements partial identification bounds without
requiring gold-standard measurements.

Version: 0.1.0.9000

────────────────────────────────────────────────

Next: Complete vignettes, prepare for CRAN submission
